      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... it's not just being tired. it's the feeling that there's no actual future. no version of my life where this stops. it feels like i'm just trapped in this cycle of agony. sometimes i look at death and i don't see something scary, i just see peace. like, wouldn't it be more merciful to just stop the noise?",
